{"tid":147625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違法向伊出售美國技術　中國中興吞天價罰金","createTime":"2017-03-08T03:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T06:25:25.000Z","uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28d0a34d230a4819302a87051239cac2d80f59bc","tid":147625,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"違法向伊出售美國技術　中國中興吞天價罰金 (乜唔係中國自煮研發高科技咩？)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170308/1071388/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170308%2F1071388%2F&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=3b4fb8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170308/1071388/</a> <br />\n中國第2大通訊設備製造商中興通訊就伊朗制裁案與美國當局達成和解，罰金加上資產沒收金額最高可達12億美元（370億台幣）。中興今在深圳臨時停牌，稱因發生受到處罰的重大無先例事項。 <br />\n<br />\n中興通訊已同意認罪，並為違反美國出口管制法律，向伊朗出售美國技術的行為，支付高達12億美元的罰沒金。 <br />\n<br />\n認罪協議中要求的罰款和資產罰沒金額共計8.92億美元；另外，若是違反協議條款，還將被額外處以3億美元罰款。這是美國司法部迄今在出口管制制裁案上開出的最大金額的刑事罰單。 <br />\n<br />\n美國司法部長塞森（Jeff Sessions）在聲明中表示：「中興不但違反禁止向伊朗等敵意政權出售美國技術的出口管制法，還在其違法行為問題上向聯邦調查人員撒謊，甚至欺騙自己的法律顧問與內部調查人員。這份協議認定其應當承擔責任，並明確表明，我們的政府會使用手中的一切工具對違反我國法律的公司施以懲戒。」 <br />\n<br />\n中興將對3項重罪指控予以認罪：違反出口管制法、作出嚴重虛假陳述、妨礙司法。認罪協議還需得到法院的認可。 <br />\n<br />\n據深圳證券交易所公告，中興通訊今日開市起臨時停牌，待公司充分與投資人溝通並刊登相關公告後復牌。（于倩若／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"3e7aad70e69ed82297e93e01fe41f0a43ea99090","tid":147625,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"留名睇ZTE俾美帝罰完再罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1922785f5e76d841ba633c79226001996cfbfe","tid":147625,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"中國狗就係咁賤"},{"pid":"ed2c905356e85b107bcb429d4ec8138c36a8d389","tid":147625,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"支那政府再出聲就罰多幾億美金"},{"pid":"bbe77f9162e6e3de38bac9977865f495b24c1270","tid":147625,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"轉過頭，支那又搵高通開刀，遲下連蘋果都開埋。"},{"pid":"8bceece89f749bd4a977153ef515059f4c2c02f4","tid":147625,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72455f88dc6c1695a5af82ebe393ae0388094cf1","tid":147625,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/122403_49d2895d734d25fea938d54b50aa7174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F08%2F122403_49d2895d734d25fea938d54b50aa7174.jpg&h=9a29b43e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"866a4cda776217bceb9aab0486e90fcebde64200","tid":147625,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c7333831f880b98c16f18330b65f988393edba","tid":147625,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287d45a9196fd8f9c7c9de3fb9d2500077b875f2","tid":147625,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"區區12億美金，伊朗根本唔當係錢! 罰太少!"},{"pid":"5dc8e4cad5e23162b8082de3cf27822ea7f3580a","tid":147625,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"俾人罰好過走資走唔切蒸撚發晒<img src